   {formatTime(duration)}","Error: Cannot access refs during render\n\nReact refs are values that are not needed for rendering. Refs should only be accessed outside of render, such as in event handlers or effects. Accessing a ref value (the `current` property) during render can cause your component not to update as expected (https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef).\n\nF:\\MosterAds\\MonsterCreative\\src\\renderer\\src\\screens\\audio-lab\\components\\UnifiedAudioPlayer.tsx:92:28\n  90 |           <div style={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between' }}>\n  91 |              <span style={{ fontSize: 10, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)', fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)' }}>\n> 92 |                {formatTime(audioRef.current?.currentTime || 0)}\n     |                            ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Cannot access ref value during render\n  93 |              </span>\n  94 |              <span style={{ fontSize: 10, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)', fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)' }}>\n  95 |                {formatTime(duration)}","Error: Cannot access refs during render\n\nReact refs are values that are not needed for rendering. Refs should only be accessed outside of render, such as in event handlers or effects. Accessing a ref value (the `current` property) during render can cause your component not to update as expected (https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef).\n\nF:\\MosterAds\\MonsterCreative\\src\\renderer\\src\\screens\\audio-lab\\components\\UnifiedAudioPlayer.tsx:92:28\n  90 |           <div style={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between' }}>\n  91 |              <span style={{ fontSize: 10, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)', fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)' }}>\n> 92 |                {formatTime(audioRef.current?.currentTime || 0)}\n     |                            ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Cannot access ref value during render\n  93 |              </span>\n  94 |              <span style={{ fontSize: 10, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)', fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)' }}>\n  95 |                {formatTime(duration)}",{"range":"21863","text":"16432"},"Replace `·<span·style={{·fontSize:·10,·color:·'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)',·fontFamily:·'var(--font-mono)'·}}` with `<span⏎··············style={{⏎················fontSize:·10,⏎················color:·'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)',⏎················fontFamily:·'var(--font-mono)'⏎··············}}⏎············`",{"range":"21864","text":"21865"},{"range":"21866","text":"16432"},{"range":"21867","text":"16432"},{"range":"21868","text":"16432"},"Replace `\"0:00\";` with `'0:00'`",{"range":"21869","text":"21870"},{"range":"21871","text":"16432"},{"range":"21872","text":"16432"},{"range":"21873","text":"16432"},{"range":"21874","text":"16432"},{"range":"21875","text":"16432"},{"range":"21876","text":"16432"},{"range":"21877","text":"16432"},{"range":"21878","text":"16432"},{"range":"21879","text":"16432"},{"range":"21880","text":"16432"},{"range":"21881","text":"16432"},{"range":"21882","text":"16432"},{"range":"21883","text":"16432"},{"range":"21884","text":"16432"},{"range":"21885","text":"16432"},{"range":"21886","text":"16432"},{"range":"21887","text":"16432"},{"range":"21888","text":"16432"},{"range":"21889","text":"16432"},{"range":"21890","text":"16432"},{"range":"21891","text":"16432"},"Replace `·id:·'generate',·path:·'/image-gen/generate',·label:·'Generate',·description:·'Create·original·ad·images·from·text·prompts',·icon:·Wand2,·color:·'#6C63FF'·},␍` with `⏎····id:·'generate',⏎····path:·'/image-gen/generate',⏎····label:·'Generate',⏎····description:·'Create·original·ad·images·from·text·prompts',⏎····icon:·Wand2,⏎····color:·'#6C63FF'⏎··},`",{"range":"21892","text":"21893"},"Replace `·id:·'vton',·path:·'/image-gen/vton',·label:·'Virtual·Try-On',·description:·'AI·Casting·Director·for·your·garments',·icon:·Shirt,·color:·'#EC4899'·},␍` with `⏎····id:·'vton',⏎····path:·'/image-gen/vton',⏎····label:·'Virtual·Try-On',⏎····description:·'AI·Casting·Director·for·your